| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0257 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8b9bd5bb-5e04-5843-82d6-3c1fc03da0ca"
